00:09:24,247 --> 00:09:27,009
I got to Skype into Birzeit University in Ramallah

210
00:09:27,009 --> 00:09:28,671
in the West Bank, which is awesome.

211
00:09:28,671 --> 00:09:30,792
I'm half Palestinian, so that was a really huge moment

212
00:09:30,792 --> 00:09:31,693
for me.

213
00:09:31,693 --> 00:09:35,436
And at the same time running workshops

214
00:09:35,436 --> 00:09:37,899
on text adventures game, text, that,

215
00:09:37,899 --> 00:09:39,260
text adventure games, there we go.

216
00:09:39,789 --> 00:09:42,110
at OCAD, York, and Ryerson University.

217
00:09:42,110 --> 00:09:46,392
So at this point, I was particularly interested

